body:
I have one big issue with blue wards at the moment: On the minimapo, they look exactly the same as normal wards, just that they don&#039;t act the same in that you can&#039;t tp on them.
More than once, i looked at the minimap, though i had a great ward for a tp-flank, recalled for the homeguard buff, and then noticed that it&#039;s a blue ward and i can&#039;t tp, so i recalled for nothing at all....

#If bluewards act differently than normal wards, they should also appear diffrently on the minimap to prevent confusion with {{summoner:12}}
